videos.headline: Jobe picks-off Rogers on first drive of the game
videos.description: Josh Jobe intercepts Will Rogers' pass to give Bama early momentum.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jobe picks-off Rogers on first drive of the game) 2021/10/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Metchie races past Bulldog's defense for the 46-yard TD
videos.description: John Metchie III shows off his RAC ability with a 46-yard touchdown catch for Alabama.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Metchie races past Bulldog’s defense for the 46-yard TD) 2021/10/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Battle answers the house call for an Alabama pick-six
videos.description: Jordan Battle gets up for the interception and returns it 40 yards for a pick-six.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Battle answers the house call for an Alabama pick-six) 2021/10/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robinson punches in 1-yard touchdown for the Crimson Tide
videos.description: Brian Robinson Jr. falls over the goal line to put Alabama up 21-3 in the 2nd quarter.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Robinson punches in 1-yard touchdown for the Crimson Tide) 2021/10/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bama wastes no time with 75-yard TD pass to start the half
videos.description: Jameson Williams hauls in a 75-yard touchdown for Alabama on the first play of the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bama wastes no time with 75-yard TD pass to start the half) 2021/10/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robinson walks into the end zone for his 2nd TD of the day
videos.description: Brian Robinson Jr. hauls in a pass from Bryce Young and runs it all the way to the end zone for the 51-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Robinson walks into the end zone for his 2nd TD of the day) 2021/10/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robinson pushes the pile, rumbles in for 3rd TD of the night
videos.description: Brian Robinson Jr. churns his legs to muscle his way to a 3-yard touchdown for Alabama.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Robinson pushes the pile, rumbles in for 3rd TD of the night) 2021/10/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young finds Holden over the middle for the 29-yard TD pass
videos.description: Bryce Young completes his fourth TD pass of the day to Traeshon Holden as Bama continue to rout.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Young finds Holden over the middle for the 29-yard TD pass) 2021/10/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young, Bama recover with statement win vs. MS State
videos.description: In response to a shocking loss against Texas A&M, QB Bryce Young (348 yards, 4 TDs) leads the No. 5 Tide to a commanding 49-9 win over Mississippi State.

videos.headline: Saban says the Crimson Tide need to keep improving
videos.description: No. 5 Alabama's Nick Saban touches on the leadership players showed this week, but says the Tide needs to keep building on the win over Mississippi State.

videos.headline: Anderson Jr. says Tide wanted to put loss behind them
videos.description: No. 5 Alabama LB Will Anderson Jr. credits his team for being focused all week at practice and explains how his mindset led him to four sacks on the night.
